-- Neo Solar Power to Buy Wafer, Polysilicon From South Korea's Osung LST
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-22T02:41:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-22/neo-solar-power-to-buy-wafer-polysilicon-from-south-korea-s-osung-lst.html
Neo Solar Power Corp. will buy 31.25
million pieces of wafers from South Korea’s Osung LST Co. from
2011 to 2013, the Taiwanese solar-cell maker said in a statement
posted on its website today.  Neo Solar Power will also procure 11,600 tons of
polysilicon from Hankook Silicon Co. from 2011 to 2017, the
company said in a seperate statement on its website. The
contract values weren’t disclosed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  